2015-06-10 12:06:48	detach-	vdemeester: i've actually been at an event, sat through a docker presentation and saw the same slide deck. i still don't see how it is different from a VM
2015-06-10 12:07:28	cpuguy83	detach-: Completely different from a VM, different goals, different technology.
