2015-06-10 12:17:48	detach-	cpuguy83: what I gather here is that docker is trying to abstract away the O/S layer
2015-06-10 12:17:58	cpuguy83	And in all this it's not about doing it "better than VM's", that's missing the point. VM's are great, they have a purpose.
